questiondata.strat-other: I would start by imagining the first word, and then using the second word to create a scene. For example, guitar, then brandy, which I would imagine the guitar leaning against a barstool, and a glass of brandy on the bar, and then each word I would place the picture of that somewhere in my scene. I also would imagine items lying around my house, couch, curtain, etc..
